Lomas Capital Management, LLC: Private Company Information - Bloomberg









































  





















































































July 25, 2017 9:49 PM ET
Capital Markets

Company Overview of Lomas Capital Management, LLC



Snapshot People




Company Overview
Lomas Capital Management, LLC is a privately owned hedge fund sponsor. The firm primarily provides its services to pooled investment vehicles. It invests in public equity markets. The firm employs long/short strategy to make its investments. It employs fundamental analysis along with bottom-up stock picking approach to create its portfolios. The firm obtains external research to make its investments. It typically invests in companies in consumer, industrial, and financial sectors. The firm was founded on January 9, 2012 and is based in New York City. Lomas Capital Management, LLC operates as a subsidiary of Lomas Capital Advisors, L.P.


500 Park Avenue4th FloorNew York, NY 10022United StatesFounded in 2012



Phone: 646-569-3200

Fax: 646-569-3201








