New York, NY, based Investment company Lomas Capital Management, LLC buys Athene Holding, BlackRock Inc, Boyd Gaming Corp, Eldorado Resorts Inc, Constellation Brands Inc, Alleghany Corp, RenaissanceRe Holdings, American National Insurance Co, trivago NV, Rush Enterprises Inc, sells Visa Inc, US Bancorp, Marsh & McLennan Inc, United Continental Holdings Inc, Manitowoc Co Inc during the 3-months ended 2017-03-31, according to the most recent filings of the investment company, Lomas Capital Management, LLC. As of 2017-03-31, Lomas Capital Management, LLC owns 32 stocks with a total value of $413 million.  These are the details of the buys and sells.New Purchases: BLK, BYD, ERI, Y, RNR, ANAT, TRVG, RUSHA, PPG, CSCO, Added Positions: ATH, STZ, BABA, HABT, Reduced Positions: TTWO, GS, TAP, BERY, SBUX, PGR, EL, EA, GOOG, MANU, Sold Out: V, USB, MMC, UAL, MTW, NFLX, SCHW, PRU, MAR, VOYA, 
ATH 30-Year Financial DataThe intrinsic value of ATHPeter Lynch Chart of ATHFor the details of Lomas Capital Management, LLC's stock buys and sells, go to http://www.gurufocus.com/StockBuy.php?GuruName=Lomas+Capital+Management%2C+LLCThese are the top 5 holdings of Lomas Capital Management, LLCAlphabet Inc (GOOG) - 56,492 shares, 11.35% of the total portfolio.  Shares reduced by 1.6%Athene Holding Ltd (ATH) - 756,722 shares, 9.16% of the total portfolio.  Shares added by 228.40%Progressive Corp (PGR) - 903,924 shares, 8.58% of the total portfolio.  Shares reduced by 8.34%Take-Two Interactive Software Inc (TTWO) - 458,455 shares, 6.58% of the total portfolio.  Shares reduced by 34.03%Lowe's Companies Inc (LOW) - 253,305 shares, 5.04% of the total portfolio.  Shares reduced by 1.32%New Purchase: BlackRock Inc (BLK)Lomas Capital Management, LLC initiated holdings in  BlackRock Inc.  The purchase prices were between $371.64 and $397.81, with an estimated average price of $382.53.   The stock is now traded at around $385.12. The impact to the portfolio due to this purchase was 3.61%. The holdings were 38,819 shares as of 2017-03-31. New Purchase: Boyd Gaming Corp (BYD)Lomas Capital Management, LLC initiated holdings in  Boyd Gaming Corp.  The purchase prices were between $19.34 and $22.01, with an estimated average price of $20.31.   The stock is now traded at around $24.80. The impact to the portfolio due to this purchase was 2.61%. The holdings were 490,266 shares as of 2017-03-31. New Purchase: Eldorado Resorts Inc (ERI)Lomas Capital Management, LLC initiated holdings in  Eldorado Resorts Inc.  The purchase prices were between $15.1 and $19.7, with an estimated average price of $16.86.   The stock is now traded at around $20.70. The impact to the portfolio due to this purchase was 2.53%. The holdings were 550,930 shares as of 2017-03-31. New Purchase: Alleghany Corp (Y)Lomas Capital Management, LLC initiated holdings in  Alleghany Corp.  The purchase prices were between $599.5 and $656.22, with an estimated average price of $623.74.   The stock is now traded at around $571.13. The impact to the portfolio due to this purchase was 1.98%. The holdings were 13,317 shares as of 2017-03-31. New Purchase: RenaissanceRe Holdings Ltd (RNR)Lomas Capital Management, LLC initiated holdings in  RenaissanceRe Holdings Ltd.  The purchase prices were between $135.67 and $150.35, with an estimated average price of $143.09.   The stock is now traded at around $136.91. The impact to the portfolio due to this purchase was 1.75%. The holdings were 49,910 shares as of 2017-03-31. New Purchase: American National Insurance Co (ANAT)Lomas Capital Management, LLC initiated holdings in  American National Insurance Co.  The purchase prices were between $114.35 and $124.45, with an estimated average price of $119.38.   The stock is now traded at around $115.70. The impact to the portfolio due to this purchase was 1.75%. The holdings were 61,199 shares as of 2017-03-31. Added: Athene Holding Ltd (ATH)Lomas Capital Management, LLC added to the holdings in  Athene Holding Ltd by 228.40%.  The purchase prices were between $45.9 and $53.72, with an estimated average price of $49.61.   The stock is now traded at around $52.99. The impact to the portfolio due to this purchase was 6.37%. The holdings were 756,722 shares as of 2017-03-31. Added: Constellation Brands Inc (STZ)Lomas Capital Management, LLC added to the holdings in  Constellation Brands Inc by 116.87%.  The purchase prices were between $146.75 and $164.61, with an estimated average price of $155.87.   The stock is now traded at around $178.57. The impact to the portfolio due to this purchase was 2.52%. The holdings were 119,098 shares as of 2017-03-31. Sold Out: Visa Inc (V)Lomas Capital Management, LLC sold out the holdings in  Visa Inc.  The sale prices were between $79.5 and $90.24, with an estimated average price of $86.02. Sold Out: US Bancorp (USB)Lomas Capital Management, LLC sold out the holding